Class GearDriveExtend

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Command
      • org.usfirst.frc.team5957.robot.commands.geardrive.GearDriveExtend
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class GearDriveExtend
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Command
    Command that pushes or pulls a gear with the screw conveyor. By default, expires after 3 seconds and pushes at full speed.
